Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:07.77,CN_ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\xshad2\yshad4}那是一片碎裂的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:14.47,CN_ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\xshad2\yshad4}我們是那曲旋律
